00:27:27.000 --> 00:27:28.099
"Tertawa"

725
00:27:29.470 --> 00:27:30.640
"Sementara itu, Joo Hyuk pergi ke pusat kota"

726
00:27:30.640 --> 00:27:32.140
Kenapa kamu memilihku?

