823
00:32:20.289 --> 00:32:21.630
Karena itu mengambil semua nutrisi.

824
00:32:24.000 --> 00:32:25.799
"Melihat sekeliling"

825
00:32:26.470 --> 00:32:28.470
"Di mana putraku?"

826
00:32:28.740 --> 00:32:31.269
